projects.name: S5 Real Estate
projects.description: It is built with the MERN stack-powered platform for seamless buying, selling, and management of real estate properties. Robust backend technology meets a dynamic frontend interface in S5 Real Estates digital platform. Simplifying real estate transactions with user-friendly features, S5 offers a comprehensive solution for property enthusiasts with the implementation of an AI chat bot.

projects.name: Bangalore House Price Predictions
projects.description: A web app utilising machine learning and flask for accurate property price estimates in Bangalore, India. Advanced algorithms and real estate data power the Bangalore House Price Predictions web app, aiding users in competitive housing market decisions. An invaluable tool for buyers and sellers, offering precise property price forecasts through machine learning in the bustling Bangalore real estate market.
